{"tid":1311780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［沙田遊行］聽日沙田遊行記得帶齊物質呀！！！","createTime":"2019-07-13T10:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T11:18:55.000Z","uid":78559,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc7fd2b881be80d18c138928ae0312221b3b37b","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"鑑於77旺角同今日上水嘅遊行<br />\n和平遊行最後都變成動武<br />\n各位手足聽日要準備好要準備嘅野！<br />\n保護自己！<br />\n有咩事拖實身邊嘅人！"},{"pid":"51a06d2ea40172ad2192014cbef2a3b20ff19e73","tid":1311780,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化"},{"pid":"0370bccdb2de2bf51f53fceda3e1bed4909b0ddf","tid":1311780,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n呼嘰呀"},{"pid":"d3d5f853d62b368f4a1e5bb1dc24bd8c2877d862","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e730ab04582649ebb27cecba2bbdba6c61db6523","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:44:33.000Z","msg":"聽日沙田遊行full gear"},{"pid":"06bbbcfad62173197bf3addb3a4f2977775016a7","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6c6234c7b3fe56e5a6d1220a928f1c1631a656c","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e400131c650d1da4a8a4fa037c14fe8e740b52","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8169487f50c8b69e7ff7dd4aef5ea121cd010551","tid":1311780,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB